outh Africans, wherever they are in the world.\", \"from\": 4528, \"to\": 4649, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4561, \"end\": 4573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999993669917, \"rank\": 6.330157629615607e-10, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are independent.No agenda.No bias.\", \"from\": 4651, \"to\": 4688, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our offices are for administrative purposes only, no visitors will be accepted without an appointment.\", \"from\": 4690, \"to\": 4792, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"South Africa- Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd - Registration Number: 2005/028472/07 - Address: Regus Business Centre, 1st Floor, Block B, North Park, Black River Park, 2 Fir Street, Observatory, Cape Town, 7925, South Africa  Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 4794, \"to\": 5083, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4932, \"end\": 4942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newcastle_Great_Park\", \"score\": 0.9998075148317765, \"rank\": 0.00019252222571353777, \"text\": \"North Park\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newcastle_Great_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newcastle_Great_Park\"}, {\"begin\": 4976, \"end\": 4998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Observatory,_Cape_Town\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Observatory, Cape Town\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Observatory,_Cape_Town\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Observatory,_Cape_Town\"}, {\"begin\": 5006, \"end\": 5018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999993669917, \"rank\": 6.330157629615607e-10, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"d